---
title: Prawn Wontons & Sweet Soy Egg Noodles with Broccoli Florets, Asian Greens & Sesame Seeds
description: These prawn and chive wontons are a new favourite, we want to add them to all our recipes! For this one we’ve paired them with sticky sweet egg noodles in a rich, glossy sauce with veggies mixed through. Don’t forget the sprinkle of sesame seeds for added crunch!
